msgctxt "456"
msgid "Troubled Employee"
msgstr "Empleado con Problemas"

msgctxt "460"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "84_Troubled Employee"
msgid "Some gang kept hanging around our old location and getting in the way of business. We had to move because of it."
msgstr "Una pandilla se la pasaba rondando por nuestro antiguo local y nos perjudicaba el negocio. Por eso tuvimos que reubicarnos."

msgctxt "96_Troubled Employee"
msgid "I wish we could get rid of them and go back to our old spot."
msgstr "Ojalá pudiéramos deshacernos de ellos y regresar a nuestro antiguo lugar."

